HEADWORD: Lithogenesy
<hw>Lith`o*gen"e*sy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Litho-</ets> Gr. <grk>ge`nesis</grk> origin, generation: cf.
F. <ets>lithog⟦eacute⟧n⟦eacute⟧sie</ets>. See <er>Genesis</er>.]</ety>
<def>The doctrine or science of the origin of the minerals composing the
globe.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

